Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文…歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏…香？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦 文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  请过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,301室的美川文歌苏醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒过来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子如果醒来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把枪  是射杀你父亲的那把枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是这次文伽要送的死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那种东西送去要干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她用这个开枪射我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽的玩笑真无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员已经是死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被射了的话也死不了的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小文的另一个人格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果小文否定了我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我则会死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌的女儿苏醒过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 刚才医院那边联络的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易美川老师的新书要发行的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虐待女儿的事情如果被人披露的话就出版不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川文歌苏醒过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后遗症的情况到目前还没有发现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体方面也很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是记忆好像很模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么有关当时事件的印象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是记不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不可以操之过急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  询问的话也得等她恢复好以后的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后现在情况如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟朋友聊天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔来探望的孩子今天正好也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学时在一起的…虽然只有半年而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初是在保健室见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我游泳课的时候  伤了脚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢回想就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你记得我的名字啊  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌会死?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘文歌’是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是邮递员这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽是为了消失掉才做邮递员的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是为了赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赎罪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她认为那边的文歌之所以变成睡美人  是自己造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌向文伽开枪的话  双重人格就会消除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就意味着邮递员的文伽会死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是文伽她自己想要这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么千章你要来到这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千章也不希望文歌消失的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  等下啊  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信地址可是港口那边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看过小文之后才去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成工作之后不也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去送信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隐约感觉到她在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫着‘美歌’
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已经晚了  明天再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  把蛋壳放里面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客气  尽管吃饱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  今天的肉也太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算因为有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  又不是昭和年代的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑啦  这不是惯例吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香的玩笑好老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对着现役青春活泼的女高中生在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  现役青春活泼的这词就已经很老了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  什么啊大家一起笑话我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  暂时避免了两人见面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为检查转移到别的医院去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查?  难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么病变啦  只是尝试下新的治疗方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  一周之后就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那块可是我一直看着的肉哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  一不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的肉这么鲜嫩好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子她妈大出血了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  看出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛肉火锅果然还是得用和牛肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是第一次吃牛肉火锅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夹来喜欢吃的东西  然后蘸着鸡蛋吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千钧一发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后文歌马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你处理的还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算都好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许硬拉她来我家是做对了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌她好像从来都没有跟大家一起吃过饭  玩过游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  或者这样更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这么做也就是延迟些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  千章姊说过她有办法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借给我你的力量  莉莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福音局的法律你知道的很详细的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难得啊  千章竟然来求别人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就说明我有多着急了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不确定能不能助你一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过先听你说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在你隔壁的房间  有什么事情随时叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲敲墙的话也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱呢  文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  把她带来做对了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到她会那么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实她比外表看起来小多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:11:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果文歌治好了的话  她别的人格会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像会合成一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合成一个?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然表面上看着是消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也会深深地留在那个人的心中的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在文化祭上一鸣惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要就成了Miss海鸥中学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些事就别提了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生们男扮女装
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该留有照片的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说是被强迫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说真的相当漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要做  就不想输啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到一个  相似点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…夹哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  美川
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打赢了架  露出男孩子一般的神情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啦  你刚醒过来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来  慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事  如今不要再让我想起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赎罪就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间也好  金钱也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为  我为了争取被判无罪花了多少精力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与法律无关
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心灵背负的罪孽只能由心灵来赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  回家吧回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的文歌还没回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就直接…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我下啦  文伽  你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找小文转院的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:14:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封死后文  非寄不可吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非寄不可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  很喜欢文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一说想变成人  大家都笑话我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有文伽没笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还跟我说‘加油’
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想和文伽做搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后也一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  卡娜卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是对我的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须接受惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我送完他去车站就回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像…是从这…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个文歌…合为一体比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说美歌消失也没所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不知道才问你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要  夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你怎么旁若无人地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看到文伽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在房间里  到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽和文歌都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对父亲…开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条裁决能派上用场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13年后的判决就可以推翻它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这个说不定可以用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说能救她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能  可以把她的存在作为特例承认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌  你在哪  美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:17:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美  歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美歌  美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年不见了  小文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  对父亲…开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕  好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  该道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为对煌开枪的  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小文沉睡的这三年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见到了很多人  见过了各式各样的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也得到了很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小文的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错的是我  和煌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  朝我开枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样  一切就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌  你在这种地方干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得说不定能想起点什么  就想在街上走走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你见到什么人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  谁也没碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你特地过来  真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是询问  你也不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生  我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起诉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要起诉我的父亲  美川煌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次  由我来开枪
