Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.85,0:23:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一连串的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是未来
